Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:13.973 --> 02:15.874
Erika!

02:16.976 --> 02:19.845
This is a surprise.

02:19.847 --> 02:21.313
Hello, all.

02:21.315 --> 02:23.948
Sorry to intrude.

02:23.950 --> 02:25.683
Hi, honey.

02:27.886 --> 02:29.787
Wow, it's really
good to see you.

02:29.789 --> 02:31.255
Uh...

02:31.257 --> 02:33.290
Did we have plans
to get together?

02:33.292 --> 02:36.294
I have some news
that couldn't wait.

02:36.296 --> 02:38.096
Okay.

02:38.098 --> 02:40.399
I wanted to tell you
in person...

02:40.401 --> 02:41.968
Great, good.

02:41.970 --> 02:43.269
It's just that we have
this U.N. inspection team

02:43.271 --> 02:44.904
due in an hour,

02:44.906 --> 02:47.041
and I'm installing this
whole new mirror array

02:47.043 --> 02:48.209
so that they can access our
system without actually--

02:48.211 --> 02:50.077
Henry.

02:51.346 --> 02:52.380
Stopping?

02:54.050 --> 02:55.417
Listening.

03:02.959 --> 03:04.126
You're going to be a father.

03:10.466 --> 03:11.332
Oh.

03:16.205 --> 03:20.205
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Sanctuary 4x03 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Untouchable</font>
